metadata.dcterms:title: One-time Payments for Books, by Vendor
metadata.dcterms:creator: University of Alberta Libraries
metadata.dcterms:description: This data represents one-time payments for books (print and electronic) for the University of Alberta Libraries for the 2014 through 2021 fiscal years (April - March), with expenditure information provided per vendor.
